snippet.title: Wilson: In Search of Tom
snippet.description:
Its a Unity made game that's uploaded on here: 

kuraisensei.itch.io/wilson-in-search-of-tom

It was meant to be a GameJam Game but I ended up working on it a bit more just so its a bit more playable, now its far more enjoyable (just imagine how bad the original was) 

Feel free to play and give me some feed back, would mean alot

Also feel free to check out my other games on kuraisensei.itch.io

And/ or check my Website and Social media:
kuraisensei.wixsite.com/kurai-sa
